snippet.title: Darksiders Genesis -  Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Coming to consoles on February 14, 2020

(sing along to Paul Young's Love is in the Air)
Love is in the air, everywhere we look around,
Mercy and Redemption, make that satisfying sound,
And if Strife does not get you, War will,
Chaoseater needs some blood to spill,
This is something that we all believe in,
And it's there when we look in your eyes

https://darksiders.com/

#togetherthroughhell
#GunsNHorses
#notalone
